fields.description:
As a user, I will see the patient weight history.


The user will be able to add the weight history of the patient:
\-The user will need to fill in the weight history info: Date, Weight and Comment
After each session, the patient’s weight will be added automatically
The user will be able to delete an history item from the list
The history items list will be sorted by their date.

The user will see on the graph the weight timeline of the patient’s:
While the user is hovering on a timeline dot, he will see the weight info at the timeline.

The user will see also a graph of the Ahuzon.

The user will save his edits by tapping the save button.
